唔知做緊乜同完全冇合作過"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T05:56:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />民主黨賣港就梗嘅<br />\n講經咩 <br />\n<br />\n人地都唔玩35plus<br />\n唔該你唔好咁癲啦<br />\n<br />\n你搵返啲玩35plus嘅政黨自己閂埋門玩初選雷動玩飽佢啦<br />\n呢個世界唔係得連登架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b22e3f3d6fec03f241e6f010af39c30f66701a3","tid":2059643,"uid":139516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T06:00:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gzD6APC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgzD6APC.png&h=161a66bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3d79e34ec6182de7b63d36466c1f062b8b0ac3d","tid":2059643,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T06:05:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75bebae15c7e0d5088288b88dcaa2fdcddc45595","tid":2059643,"uid":187664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62d3d12935b0c38b6521c0f5f13296898995ede7","tid":2059643,"uid":139516,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c15d19de01cf68dd10e8af2503ca9e1c66bb758c","tid":2059643,"uid":139516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T05:22:54.000Z","msg":"【墨落無悔 堅定抗爭】<br />\n<br />\n【抗爭派立場聲明書】<br />\n<br />\n昨日（6月9日），戴耀廷教授召開記者會交待初選細節，表示不會要求參選人簽署共同綱領。<br />\n<br />\n我們認為，在初選協調會議上已取得共識的共同綱領，乃一眾參選人之合作基礎。考慮到立場差異，此一綱領已達致抗爭陣營光譜的最大公因數。墨落理應無悔，否則等於失信於選民。<br />\n<br />\n我們呼籲有意參與初選者，在宣布參選時公開簽署以下聲明：<br />\n<br />\n「<br />\n1. 我認同『五大訴求，缺一不可』。我會運用基本法賦予立法會的權力，包括否決財政預算案，迫使特首回應五大訴求，撤銷所有抗爭者控罪，令相關人士為警暴問責，並重啟政改達致雙普選。<br />\n<br />\n2. 我認同若支持度跌出各區預計可得議席範圍，須表明停止選舉工程。<br />\n」<br />\n<br />\n我們深明議會絕非抗爭終點，以上聲明，僅為確保抗爭陣營參選人，有最基本的抗爭意志。<br />\n<br />\n我們的抗爭決心，絕不應因極權打壓而讓步。我們呼籲各位香港人，拒絕支持抗爭意志飄忽不定的參選人。<br />\n<br />\n鄒家成<br />\n張可森<br />\n梁晃維<br />\n黃子悅<br />\n劉頴匡<br />\n朱凱廸<br />\n岑敖暉<br />\n何桂藍<br />\n彭卓棋<br />\n張崑陽<br />\n王百羽<br />\n吳敏兒<br />\n楊雪盈<br />\n陳志全<br />\n譚得志<br />\n郭永健<br />\n劉澤鋒<br />\n馮達浚<br />\n余慧明<br />\n曾健超<br />\n林進<br />\n柯耀林<br />\n施德來<br />\n何啟明<br />\n呂智恆<br />\n公民黨<br />\n<br />\n（名單更新時間：11/06/2020 13:16）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><em>鄒家成真係叻仔嚟，俾佢夾到班泛民</em></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T05:23:20.000Z","msg":"民主黨呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T06:06:33.000Z","msg":"出邊籌緊旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"665cb8530c7976484be2c6e828671b11f010be3a","tid":2059643,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T06:13:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}